title: Boring my friend
author: MineHero96
pages:
#- With this Book and quill I thought I'd write
A Tale that could, shine some light.
On the one that they call 'Boring'. 
 BoringNumbers123 the toughest guy you'll ever see. He will slay you all with his Fire Aspect I Sharp III.
#- He is my Best friend On civcraft, If you dont know him you must be daft (Stupid), He is the kindest guy I know on here and being nice does not make him queer. Yes we used to share a house but then I had to move for INF-A-MOUS. Who is our good friend too,
#- He lives with Pablo or
Ha-roo! The four of us all have a laugh,
these laughs go on past civcraft, we play together on CivPvP where we hold battles worthy of History, we also play on Feed the Beast "I still want my Jetpack please!" 
#- Theres a server called HCF and everyone knows we are'nt the best and we always get a 3 day ban, "Which is worse than when I got taken into that old man's van"....... But thats another story
#- Anyway I have come to an end, Boring you really are my true friend! :D

By Scott
P.S LUV U GARRETT
